  - characterName: Dee Bug
    dialogueText: 1TS ST1LL N3W, PLUS 1T D34LS M0R3 D4M4G3 = :(
    textColor: {r: 0.51572317, g: 0.23714338, b: 0, a: 1}
    isPlayer: 0
    messageSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2310fdff703bd2c4db3c4c2930812960, type: 3}
    delayAfter: 1.37
    isContinuation: 0
    wordHighlights: []
    showAttachedObject: 0
    attachedObjectPrefab: {fileID: 0}
    attachedObjectDelay: 0
    destroyOnNextMessage: 0
  - characterName: Handler
    dialogueText: Indeed, which is why I'm banning you.
    textColor: {r: 1, g: 0.92156863, b: 0.015686275, a: 1}
    isPlayer: 0
    messageSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2310fdff703bd2c4db3c4c2930812960, type: 3}
    delayAfter: 4
    isContinuation: 0
    wordHighlights: []
    showAttachedObject: 0
    attachedObjectPrefab: {fileID: 0}
    attachedObjectDelay: 0
    destroyOnNextMessage: 0
  - characterName: Dee Bug
    dialogueText: W04H W04H WH4T?!
    textColor: {r: 0.51572317, g: 0.23714338, b: 0, a: 1}
    isPlayer: 0
    messageSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2310fdff703bd2c4db3c4c2930812960, type: 3}
    delayAfter: 1.37
    isContinuation: 0
    wordHighlights: []
    showAttachedObject: 0
    attachedObjectPrefab: {fileID: 0}
    attachedObjectDelay: 0
    destroyOnNextMessage: 0
  - characterName: Dee Bug
    dialogueText: 1 H3LP3D Y0U! 4ND R00K13!
    textColor: {r: 0.51572317, g: 0.23714338, b: 0, a: 1}
    isPlayer: 0
    messageSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2310fdff703bd2c4db3c4c2930812960, type: 3}
    delayAfter: 1.37
    isContinuation: 0
    wordHighlights: []
    showAttachedObject: 0
    attachedObjectPrefab: {fileID: 0}
    attachedObjectDelay: 0
    destroyOnNextMessage: 0
  - characterName: Handler
    dialogueText: If they found out that you were here, ban is not the only thing
      you'll get.
    textColor: {r: 1, g: 0.92156863, b: 0.015686275, a: 1}
    isPlayer: 0
    messageSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2310fdff703bd2c4db3c4c2930812960, type: 3}
    delayAfter: 4
    isContinuation: 0
    wordHighlights: []
    showAttachedObject: 0
    attachedObjectPrefab: {fileID: 0}
    attachedObjectDelay: 0
    destroyOnNextMessage: 0
  - characterName: Handler
    dialogueText: I had talked with the higher ups and they revealed the plan was
      leaked.
    textColor: {r: 1, g: 0.92156863, b: 0.015686275, a: 1}
    isPlayer: 0
    messageSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2310fdff703bd2c4db3c4c2930812960, type: 3}
    delayAfter: 3
    isContinuation: 0
    wordHighlights: []
    showAttachedObject: 0
    attachedObjectPrefab: {fileID: 0}
    attachedObjectDelay: 0
    destroyOnNextMessage: 0
  - characterName: Handler
    dialogueText: So although you were a great help, you can get accised as a suspect
      just for being here.
    textColor: {r: 1, g: 0.92156863, b: 0.015686275, a: 1}
    isPlayer: 0
    messageSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2310fdff703bd2c4db3c4c2930812960, type: 3}
    delayAfter: 3
    isContinuation: 0
    wordHighlights: []
    showAttachedObject: 0
    attachedObjectPrefab: {fileID: 0}
    attachedObjectDelay: 0
    destroyOnNextMessage: 0
  - characterName: Handler
    dialogueText: And knowing you once had an affliation with Lady Bug, it's not
      helping your case.
    textColor: {r: 1, g: 0.92156863, b: 0.015686275, a: 1}
    isPlayer: 0
    messageSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2310fdff703bd2c4db3c4c2930812960, type: 3}
    delayAfter: 3
    isContinuation: 0
    wordHighlights: []
    showAttachedObject: 0
    attachedObjectPrefab: {fileID: 0}
    attachedObjectDelay: 0
    destroyOnNextMessage: 0
  - characterName: Dee Bug
    dialogueText: = :(
    textColor: {r: 0.51572317, g: 0.23714338, b: 0, a: 1}
    isPlayer: 0
    messageSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2310fdff703bd2c4db3c4c2930812960, type: 3}
    delayAfter: 1
    isContinuation: 0
    wordHighlights: []
    showAttachedObject: 0
    attachedObjectPrefab: {fileID: 0}
    attachedObjectDelay: 0
    destroyOnNextMessage: 0
  - characterName: Dee Bug
    dialogueText: 1M N0T 3V3N 4 BL4CK H4T 4NYM0R3 = :(
    textColor: {r: 0.51572317, g: 0.23714338, b: 0, a: 1}
    isPlayer: 0
    messageSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2310fdff703bd2c4db3c4c2930812960, type: 3}
    delayAfter: 5
    isContinuation: 0
    wordHighlights: []
    showAttachedObject: 0
    attachedObjectPrefab: {fileID: 0}
    attachedObjectDelay: 0
    destroyOnNextMessage: 0
  - characterName: Handler
    dialogueText: That still can be suspicious.
    textColor: {r: 1, g: 0.92156863, b: 0.015686275, a: 1}
    isPlayer: 0
    messageSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2310fdff703bd2c4db3c4c2930812960, type: 3}
    delayAfter: 3
    isContinuation: 0
    wordHighlights: []
    showAttachedObject: 0
    attachedObjectPrefab: {fileID: 0}
    attachedObjectDelay: 0
    destroyOnNextMessage: 0
  - characterName: Handler
    dialogueText: So if I were you, i'd rather get banned than accused.
    textColor: {r: 1, g: 0.92156863, b: 0.015686275, a: 1}
    isPlayer: 0
    messageSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2310fdff703bd2c4db3c4c2930812960, type: 3}
    delayAfter: 3
    isContinuation: 0
    wordHighlights: []
    showAttachedObject: 0
    attachedObjectPrefab: {fileID: 0}
    attachedObjectDelay: 0
    destroyOnNextMessage: 0
  - characterName: Handler
    dialogueText: Besides, this conversation will get deleted anyways. Goodbye.
    textColor: {r: 1, g: 0.92156863, b: 0.015686275, a: 1}
    isPlayer: 0
    messageSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2310fdff703bd2c4db3c4c2930812960, type: 3}
    delayAfter: 3
    isContinuation: 0
    wordHighlights: []
    showAttachedObject: 0
    attachedObjectPrefab: {fileID: 0}
    attachedObjectDelay: 0
    destroyOnNextMessage: 0
  - characterName: Dee Bug
    dialogueText: W3LP, CY4 I GUESS
    textColor: {r: 0.51572317, g: 0.23714338, b: 0, a: 1}
